=Description=

June 2008 status by Tere Vaden:

"The first protos are being built right now, and first customer deliveries are planned for next winter. The idea is '''to buy old Toyota Corollas from Germany and retrofit them with electric motors. The design is open, so anyone can do the conversion themselves''' and there is also a company that is willing to do it if a batch of 500 customers commit themselves."


